"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e5b7896a48cf5878961f1528eaf14a5d402a1b","tid":1603161,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:00.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"9312fb00c0b77a9e1083a52ddc5832e2f6bde5af","tid":1603161,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:12.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"2c4bdb500e60f9dd6956ae51a8883036a5292066","tid":1603161,"uid":37596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"612基金爆硬, 連登仔仲話唔俾生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dc8344c63fdc2efb3006b823b3cc2e5db4ba48","tid":1603161,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0eda804f78f8fca37d6cb8074b9f883d4193090b","tid":1603161,"uid":13586,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"三個月喇<br />\n<br />\n由be water，到Hit and run，到而家獅鳥召喚，最後原來都仲停留喺<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>走走走，見人走我就走</strong></span>，後面半gear同和理非嚇到雞飛狗走都唔知咩事，搞到走散哂，前線好易缺人！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n要退眼望前<br />\n不說走走走，試說急步行<br />\n不說跑呀衝緊埋黎，試說一二一二<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，三個月資訊都仲停留喺嗰邊有狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>邊度嗰邊！防暴便衣定速龍！數量！</strong></span><br />\n咁模糊嘅資訊好難叫大家部署，然後又係一味走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我要時地人一句過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不說嗰邊有狗，試說鵝頸橋五十防暴<br />\n不說呢邊有狗，試說海富橋四十速龍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有明明橋上得十幾隻狗，橋底過百甚至過千手足<br />\n都係一味叫走<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">都冇人獅鳥冇人踢波<br />\n十月一號仲點樣賀佢老母呀，得把口</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不說有狗走呀，試說有冇人踢波</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"58d8585481cc1e3d1de75750bdcd7efc3f4056d9","tid":1603161,"uid":4151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yeung.raymond/videos/10215860065554638/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyeung.raymond%2Fvideos%2F10215860065554638%2F&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=28a60145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yeung.raymond/videos/10215860065554638/</a><br />\n<br />\n你睇下咁樣都拉得唔過百就假啦"},{"pid":"f6600cd69abc51b35cc11cec3fa114839e5a5a27","tid":1603161,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:28:19.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"5c2ab8117954f2c288a311161fdf136ddfb11e2c","tid":1603161,"uid":179165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c4bdb500e60f9dd6956ae51a8883036a5292066","tid":1603161,"uid":37596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"612基金爆硬, 連登仔仲話唔俾生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"再捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b54b0f9392509454026abd2dd9995d2adacf3b","tid":1603161,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"太少喇"},{"pid":"b3811fa1d7b523b80d4cbc8942cb9037896b50d0","tid":1603161,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eda804f78f8fca37d6cb8074b9f883d4193090b","tid":1603161,"uid":13